Waters Miners of Trebulon is a game made in 48 hours for a playful competition on #blender.fi on Freenode.

It's a game in which you set up water drilling stations and try to harvest precious water.

Released under Creative Commons NC-SA.

song_game.ogg is "Lasting Hope" by Kevin Macleod
Lasting Hope by Kevin MacLeod is licensed under a CC Attribution 3.0.
http://incompetech.com/music/royalty-free/index.html?isrc=USUAN1100178.
Permissions beyond the scope of this license are available at http://incompetech.com/music/royalty-free/licenses/.

Libraries used:
C++11 (requires shared_ptr and thread)
SFML 2.0 http://www.sfml-dev.org/
libnoise http://libnoise.sourceforge.net/

